data.description: This beautiful 3 bed/2 bath split floor plan home on the cul de sac is move in ready and waiting on a new owner. You will love everything about this home from it's oversized driveway all the way back to the screened in patio inside of a private, fully fenced large back yard. For the cook of the home there is no worries with the 2021 appliance suite, new sink fixtures, eat on bar and double pantry. This easy maintenance home features the convenience of vinyl outside while the main living areas have vinyl plank and tile flooring for quick clean up. Do you need a place to store your items? We have that taken care of with a finished garage and out back there is a storage shed that will hold the yard items. The cherry on top is that we have a 2018 survey and washer/dryer can convey with offer.
